
* Windows 
  |------------------------+-------|
  | Command                | Key   |
  |------------------------+-------|
  | (split-window-below)   | C-x 2 |
  | (split-window-right)   | C-x 3 |
  | (delete-other-windows) | C-x 1 |
  | (delete-window)        | C-x 0 |
  | (other-window)         | C-x o |
  |------------------------+-------|

* Panes
  |----------------------------------+---------------------------------------+-------|
  | Info                             | Command                               | Key   |
  |----------------------------------+---------------------------------------+-------|
  | Increase Height                  | (enlarge-window)                      | C-x ^ |
  | Decrease Height                  | (shrink-window)                       |       |
  | Increase Width                   | (enlarge-window-horizontally)         | C-x } |
  | Decrease Width                   | (shrink-window-horizontally)          | C-x { |
  | Shrink window to fit its content | (shrink-window-if-larger-than-buffer) | C-x - |
  | Make all windows same height     | (balance-windows)                     | C-x + |
  |----------------------------------+---------------------------------------+-------|

* Buffers

  |---------------------+-------------------+-----------|
  | Info                | Command           | Key       |
  |---------------------+-------------------+-----------|
  | List buffers        | (list-buffers)    | C-x b C-b |
  | Switching to buffer | (switch-to-buffer | C-x b     |
  |---------------------+-------------------+-----------|
